CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "The Ole Ball Game - approximately three thousand hometown rooters saw Gus Greenlee's Pittsburgh Crawfords return to "big-time" baseball at Forbes Field last Sunday afternoon. The local boys split a doubleheader with the Brooklyn Brown Dodgers - Courier Photo by Harris"
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Crawfords baseball player crossing home plate in game against the Brooklyn Brown Dodgers at Forbes Field
